reviewText: I watched these movies when I was a teenager and I liked them. I thought they were funny movies. Anyway, going to the product itself:This is a decent purchase for anyone who wants to have three movies for the value of one. You get 3 Blu rays inside one blu ray case. The video transfer of the first movie is horrendous. The other two movies are acceptable.If you want to demo the power of blu ray to your friends, these movies are not the way to go to impress them. However, if you want to get high and laugh with your friends out of sheer stupidity, this is a highly recommended set.
